        "subject": "LU-3071 obdfilter: call cfs_cap_raise() before journal start",
        "message": "LU-3071 obdfilter: call cfs_cap_raise() before journal start\n\ncfs_cap_raise() may allocate memory and result in page flush on\ndifferent fs, which could probably trigger a nested journal\nstart on different journal.\n\nThis patch moves cfs_cap_raise() before journal start.\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <yawei.niu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I6583e134c34bc437f1aa05ca9ec922c2d5441d27\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
